data.description: Welcome home to Greenfield Estates! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is located in the Aynor school district and in walking  distance to Aynor Middle School! You'll love this small, friendly neighborhood and its close proximity to Downtown Aynor and Highway 501. Entering the home, you'll be impressed by the vaulted ceilings and open concept floor plan, with morning light flooding in. The sliding glass doors lead to a generous back patio that overlooks the pond and large backyard. The home offers a split bedroom floor plan, with a spacious primary suite featuring a large, walk-in closet and en suite bathroom with soaking tub, standing shower and spacious vanity. The opposite side of the home offers two additional bedrooms, a full bathroom and convenient linen closet. The galley style kitchen has an adjacent laundry area and pantry that leads to the single car garage. The sellers are offering a credit to buyers to help with closing costs, rate buydown or for updates to the home, and this home has an assumable mortgage for the right buyer at 5.25%! Both the roof and hot water heater are only a year old, so there are no worries with this great home! Take the 3D Matterport tour and schedule your appointment today!
